<![CDATA[<table border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" height="250" width="650"><tbody><tr><td class="previewCell" style="margin: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: top; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: none; border-color: rgb(236, 236, 236);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">NCS POWERED BY THE CHALLENGE&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Become an Associate Mentor on&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">NCS with The Challenge!&nbsp;</font><br><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Name},&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">You’re receiving this because you graduated from NCS with The Challenge.&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">This summer, there’s a fantastic opportunity for some Graduates to experience NCS with The Challenge again, from a totally different point of view.&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The Challenge Society is looking for Graduates to come back and volunteer on the programme this summer. Associate Mentors work alongside staff to support NCS Participants during the NCS Real Challenge Design.&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">You will need to be committed, passionate and willing to share your own positive experiences from NCS with The Challenge.&nbsp;</font><br><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">What's in it for you?&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Get great experience of mentoring and supporting young people&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Develop a range of new skills to enhance your record of achievement / CV / UCAS application&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Experience NCS with The Challenge from another perspective: you’ll be volunteering as staff - not as a participant!&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Fast-track your Challenge with Distinction award&nbsp;</font><br><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">What are we looking for?&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Essential Qualities:&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">We need Graduates who:&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Can be a role model for this year’s participants, taking responsibility and setting the tone&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Are passionate about their experience on NCS with The Challenge and willing to share it&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Are serious about learning new skills, personally developing and making the most out of a volunteering opportunity&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Can commit to volunteering for four days during one of the NCS Real Challenge Design weeks (there are various dates and locations throughout the summer)&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Desirable Qualities:&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">It would be great if you are:&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Confident working with new people and speaking in front of groups&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Have experience of working with other young people&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Are comfortable taking a lead with things like ice breakers and group games/activities&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Whatever your level of experience, we will support you to get the most out of this role. The most important thing is that you are committed to the role.&nbsp;</font><br><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">What is the time commitment?&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Attend a three hour training session&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Attend all four days of the Real Challenge Design (you’ll be able to choose which dates you attend when you apply)&nbsp;</font><br><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Sounds great. What next?&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">&lt;a href="http://www.clicktools.com/survey?iv=2wmw7tqmkllsa&amp;q1={!Account.TCNAccountID__c}"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#00aeef"&gt;This is a link&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;<b>&nbsp;</b>to the application form where you will answer some questions. Remember to answer as fully as you can, and give yourself the best chance of being successful.&nbsp;</font><br><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Good luck!&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The Challenge Society Team&nbsp;</font><br><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The Challenge Network Ltd is registered in England and Wales, no 6845451. Registered charity no. 1129239.&nbsp;</font><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">© The Challenge Network.&nbsp;</font><br><br><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">You are receiving this email because you opted to subscribe for communications from The Challenge.</font></td></tr></tbody></table>]]></td>
